<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Remover Livro</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <h1>🗑️ Remover Livro</h1>

    <p>Tem certeza que deseja remover o livro <strong><%= book.title %></strong> de <%= book.author %>?</p>

    <form action="/books/delete/<%= book.id %>" method="POST">
        <button type="submit">Sim, Remover</button>
    </form>

    <a href="/">⬅️ Cancelar</a>
</body>
</html>